.TH ZOPEN-PAX2RPM "1" "June 2026" "zopen tools 0.8.5" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zopen-pax2rpm \- manual page for zopen-pax2rpm 0.8.5
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zopen-pax2rpm
\fI\,<pax_file> \/\fR[\fI\,options\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate an RPM spec file from a z/OS pax archive.
.SS "Arguments:"
.TP
pax_file
Path to the pax file (e.g., \fI\,/path/to/file.pax\/\fP or file.pax.Z)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-name\fR <name>
Override package name (default: extracted from filename)
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR <version>
Override version (default: extracted from filename)
.HP
\fB\-\-pkg\-version\fR <version> Override version (alternative to \fB\-\-version\fR)
.TP
\fB\-\-release\fR <release>
Override release number (default: 1)
.TP
\fB\-\-license\fR <license>
Specify license (default: Proprietary)
.TP
\fB\-\-summary\fR <summary>
Package summary (required)
.TP
\fB\-\-description\fR <desc>
Package description (default: same as summary)
.TP
\fB\-\-url\fR <url>
Project URL (default: none)
.TP
\fB\-\-requires\fR <deps>
Package dependencies (e.g., "oef >= 1.1.0")
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR <file>
Output spec file (default: <name>.spec)
.TP
\fB\-\-build\fR
Build the RPM after generating spec file (binary + source)
.TP
\fB\-\-build\-binary\fR
Build binary RPM only (faster, no source RPM)
.TP
\fB\-\-buildroot\fR <dir>
RPM build root directory (default: \fI\,~/rpmbuild\/\fP)
.TP
\fB\-\-validate\fR
Validate spec file after generation (checks syntax and runs rpmlint)
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be done without actually doing it
.TP
\fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose debug output
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Display this help message
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Display tool version
